          <li><strong>Add Proper Margins:</strong> Include realistic margins on both sides of the page — real handwriting always has margins, and adding them makes the output look much more genuine.</li>
          <li><strong>Enable Natural Variation:</strong> If the tool offers a variation or randomness setting, turn it on. Slight differences in letter size and spacing make the handwriting look less robotic.</li>
